Bonus hacks I wish I knew before 🫡

🫘 Freeze boiled lentils, pulses, chana, rajma, etc - lasts twice as long & tastes the same
🧻 Lining of tissue around mushrooms will make them less soggy
🥕 Plan to eat perishable foods earlier in the week - eg. brocolli lasts longer than spinach
🥬 Wilted greens make for good chutneys, don’t throw away
🔪 For the love of god get a vegetable chopper
